hydrogen atoms. We talked

00:02:47.530 --> 00:02:50.580
about that quite in depth, but
there are some differences now

00:02:50.580 --> 00:02:53.440
that we have more than one
electron in the atom.

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:55.770
Then something that you
probably have a lot of

00:02:55.770 --> 00:02:59.010
experience with is talking about
electron configuration

00:02:59.010 --> 00:03:01.260
and writing out the electron
